      <title>印度军队撤离时中国向马尔代夫提供军事援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-gives-maldives-military-assistance-as-indian-troops-leave</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尔代夫国防部表示，中国同意向马尔代夫提供免费军事援助，这表明在印度军队被迫离开马尔代夫几个月后，中国与北京建立了更紧密的防务关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/china-gives-maldives-military-assistance-as-indian-troops-leave</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:56:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度要求国有炼油厂以卢比支付部分石油费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/india-asks-state-owned-refiners-to-partly-pay-for-oil-in-rupees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三名炼油厂高管表示，印度储备银行已要求该国主要国有炼油厂向波斯湾供应商施压，要求其在下一财年接受至少 10% 的石油付款以卢比支付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/india-asks-state-owned-refiners-to-partly-pay-for-oil-in-rupees</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 06:51:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
